Dan Fogler https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dan_Fogler 0 Daniel Kevin Fogler (born October 20, 1976) is an American actor and writer. He has appeared in films Balls of Fury, Good Luck Chuck, Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them, Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald, and currently stars in The Walking Dead as Luke.
